OL,3,CMan posing as a taxi driver jailed for
OL,4,Craping woman decade after similar case
OL,6,FA man posing as a taxi driver who
OL,7,Flured a lone woman into his car before
OL,8,Fraping her has been jailed, over a
OL,9,Fdecade after committing a near-
OL,10,Fidentical crime.
OL,12,FFareed Issa Tariq, 43, picked up the
OL,13,Fwoman as she was waiting for a taxi
OL,14,Fafter a night out in Swindon in the
OL,15,Fearly hours of Saturday 15 April 2023.
OL,17,FThe victim booked a taxi to return
OL,18,Fhome after a night out and received
OL,19,Fconfirmation from the taxi company
OL,20,Fthat one would arrive imminently.
