OL,3,CMan posing as a taxi driver jailed for
OL,4,Craping woman decade after similar case
OL,6,FSpotting the woman, Tariq presented
OL,7,Fhimself as a taxi driver, luring the
OL,8,Fvictim into his car before driving
OL,9,Faway.
OL,11,FDuring the journey, he began touching
OL,12,Fher inappropriately despite her asking
OL,13,Fhim to stop. He then drove into a
OL,14,Flayby and raped her.
OL,16,FTariq initially claimed that he had no
OL,17,Fsexual contact with the woman, but in
OL,18,Fa later attempt to cover up his crime
OL,19,Fwhen faced with incriminating forensic
OL,20,Fevidence, he blamed the victim for his
OL,21,FDNA being present.
