OL,4,Craping woman decade after similar case
OL,6,FIn 2012, Tariq was convicted of rape
OL,7,Fafter he offered a lift to a woman
OL,8,Ffollowing a night out in Swindon,
OL,9,Fbefore driving to a secluded area and
OL,10,Fraping her.
OL,12,FLisa Garcia, Senior Crown Prosecutor
OL,13,Fwith CPS Wessex, said: "Fareed Tariq
OL,14,Fis a danger to women.
OL,16,F"Not only did he pose as a taxi driver
OL,17,Fto prey on a lone victim, Tariq then
OL,18,Fcruelly tried to blame her for his
OL,19,Fdepraved crime.
