OL,3,CMan posing as a taxi driver jailed for
OL,4,Craping woman decade after similar case
OL,6,F"The fact he committed a strikingly
OL,7,Fsimilar crime over a decade ago shows
OL,8,Fhe is devoid of remorse and remains a
OL,9,Fthreat to the public.
OL,11,F"We hope his conviction sends a clear
OL,12,Fmessage that the CPS is committed to
OL,13,Fprosecuting rape cases and that we
OL,14,Fwill always strive to deliver justice
OL,15,Ffor victims."
OL,17,FTariq has been sentenced to a total of
OL,18,F18 years in prison at Swindon Crown
OL,19,FCourt.
